org.intellimate.izou.sdk.frameworks.presence.consumer

Interface PresenceResourceUser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ContextProvider, org.intellimate.izou.identification.Identifiable, ResourceUser, ThreadPoolUser

    public interface PresenceResourceUser
extends ResourceUser, ThreadPoolUser
    utility class used interacting with information about presence obtained through resource. For events, please use the normal Listeners.

    1.0
    Author:

      • isPresent

        default boolean isPresent()
        returns a CompletableFuture containing true if present, else false. if not presence-providers were found, it returns false. Time-Outs every Provider after 500 milliseconds.
        Returns:
        a future true if present, false if not

      • isPresent

        default boolean isPresent(boolean strict)
        returns a CompletableFuture containing true if present, else false if not presence-providers were found, it returns false. Time-Outs every Provider after 500 milliseconds.
        Parameters:
        strict - true if only addons where it is highly likely that the user is around should be creating the result
        Returns:
        a future true if present, false if not
